  - operational AI
  - hooks
  - memory
abstract: >
  A practitioner framework for making LLM corrections persist across sessions.
  Contains functional scars (structured documents recording past mistakes and
  the operational rules that prevent their recurrence) and Claude Code hooks
  (Python scripts that enforce those rules automatically at inference time).
  Grounded in 163 findings extracted from 17 production session logs across
  a civil engineering operation.
